Patient object:

Attributes: aname, age, gender, contact details, allergies, medical history, current medications, emergency contact details, insurance information.
Methods: getters and setters for attributes.


Doctor object:

Attributes: name, specialization, contact details, availability.
Methods: getters and setters for attributes.


Appointment object:

Attributes: patient object, doctor object, appointment date and time, reason for appointment, prescription (if any).
Methods: getters and setters for attributes.


Medical history object:

Attributes: patient object, past illnesses, surgeries, medications, allergies, family medical history.
Methods: getters and setters for attributes.


Allergy object:

Attributes: patient object, type of allergy, severity, treatment.
Methods: getters and setters for attributes.